on December 23, 1993 pursuant to EPA's completeness criteria that are set forth in 40 CFR part 51 appendix V
<FOOTCITE>6</FOOTCITE>
 and are being proposed for approval into the SIP. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<FOOTNOTE>
