<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
</FOOTNOTE>

<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=1 -->
Both rules control the emission of VOCs from the surface coating of metal parts and products. VOCs contribute to the
